# Cloudflare Pages SPA redirect rules
# All routes → index.html (React Router handles client-side routing)

/track          /index.html     200
/login          /index.html     200
/admin/*        /index.html     200
/merchant/*     /index.html     200
/driver/*       /index.html     200
/tracking       /track          301

# Catch-all: serve index.html for all unmatched routes (SPA)
/*              /index.html     200
